<p>A new [German] edition of <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi> is to be done. Has CD anything to add or alter?</p>  
<p>JVC cites an article on cessation of breathing during mental concentration that supports Gratiolet as quoted in <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>, p. 179.</p> 
